---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions — TradingToolsHub"
  description="Terms and conditions for using TradingToolsHub, the independent trading tools comparison directory."
  canonical="https://tradingtoolshub.com/terms/"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-text">Terms & Conditions</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-2">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-10">Last updated: March 9, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using TradingToolsHub (<a href="https://tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">tradingtoolshub.com</a>), you agree to these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use the site. TradingToolsHub is operated by Cosmic Phoenix LLC, a Wyoming limited liability company.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">What We Provide</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub is an independent directory that compares trading tools, platforms, brokers, and related financial services. We provide:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Reviews and ratings of trading software and services</li>
          <li>Side-by-side feature and pricing comparisons</li>
          <li>Category-based tool listings and recommendations</li>
          <li>Educational content about trading tools and platforms</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Not Financial Advice</h2>
        <p class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-4"><strong class="text-text">Important:</strong> Nothing on TradingToolsHub constitutes financial, investment, or trading advice. Our reviews and comparisons are informational only. Trading involves substantial risk of loss and is not suitable for all investors. Always do your own due diligence before choosing a trading platform, broker, or tool. Past performance of any tool or platform is not indicative of future results.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Affiliate Relationships</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub participates in affiliate programs. Some links on our site are affiliate links, meaning we may earn a commission if you sign up or make a purchase through our links. This does not affect the price you pay. Our editorial content is independent of our affiliate relationships. We review and compare tools based on publicly available features, pricing, and our assessment criteria, regardless of whether we have an affiliate relationship with the provider. See our full <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>We make reasonable efforts to ensure the accuracy of our reviews, pricing data, and feature comparisons. However:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Pricing and features change frequently. We update our data regularly but cannot guarantee real-time accuracy.</li>
          <li>Always verify current pricing and features directly on the provider's website before making a decision.</li>
          <li>Ratings reflect our editorial assessment and methodology, which may differ from your experience.</li>
          <li>If you notice inaccurate information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:editorial@tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">editorial@tradingtoolshub.com</a> and we will update it promptly.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All original content on TradingToolsHub — including reviews, comparisons, ratings, analysis, and design — is the property of Cosmic Phoenix LLC. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without written permission. Tool names, logos, and trademarks referenced on this site belong to their respective owners.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">User Conduct</h2>
        <p>When using TradingToolsHub, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or automatically extract data from the site without permission</li>
          <li>Attempt to interfere with the site's operation or security</li>
          <li>Use the site for any illegal purpose</li>
          <li>Misrepresent your identity or affiliation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub contains links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of any third-party site. Clicking a link to a third-party site is at your own risk. We recommend reviewing the terms and privacy policy of any service before signing up.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub and Cosmic Phoenix LLC are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the site or any trading decisions made based on information found here. This includes, but is not limited to, financial losses from trading, choosing a particular broker or tool, or relying on our reviews and ratings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Newsletter</h2>
        <p>If you subscribe to our email newsletter, you consent to receiving periodic emails about trading tools, comparisons, and industry updates. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email. We will not share your email address with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised date. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Wyoming, United States, without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:editorial@tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">editorial@tradingtoolshub.com</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Cosmic Phoenix LLC<br />Wyoming, USA</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
